1. *Ček* se još uvek čeka.(The check is still being awaited.)
2. On je *ček* platio karticom.(He paid the check with a card.)
3. Pokušavam da dobijem *ček* od njega.(I'm trying to get a check from him.)
4. *Ček* je prošao.(The check has gone through.)
5. Učitelj je pogledao *ček*.(The teacher looked at the check.)
6. Moraš da proveriš da li je *ček* ispravan.(You have to check if the check is correct.)